{"title":"排队接水","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":3,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5989","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>有n个人在一个水龙头前排队接水，假如每个人的接水时间为Ti，请编程求出这n个人的一种排队顺序，使n个人的平均等待时间最小。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行为n。</p><p>第二行分别表示第一个人到第n个人的接水时间T1……Tn，每个数据输入时之间有一个空格。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>共两行。</p><p>第一行为排队顺序，即1 到 n 的一种排列；</p><p>第二行为平均等待时间（保留两位小数）。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>10</p><p>56 12 1 99 1000 234 33 55 99 812</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3 2 7 8 1 4 9 6 10 5</p><p>532.00</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>贪心算法……</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}